name: Schoolwise Gender Student List
query:
select
    school_code as "TCIL Code",
    udise as "UDISE Code",
    name_of_school as "School Name",
    district as "District",
    block as "Block",
    pin_code as "Pin Code",
    boys as "No. of Boys",
    girls as "No. of Girls",
    total_students as "Total Students"
from
    `tabSchool Survey Form`
Group BY school_code
